oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Redding Bonner Family Reunion
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Redding Bonner family reunion at the old Bonner homestead, Viola. Shown is the family gathered around a table full of food. One of the women is Mary Dodson Rutledge, the daughter of Nimrod Dodson and widow of William Rutledge.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Reunions; Families; Tables; Eating & drinking
